The fluorescence titration of R-CDs with different concentrations of Cur was performed. Fig. 4
                        A showed that the fluorescence of R-CDs decreased with the concentration of Cur increased (0–70 μM). The linearity of F0-F/F0 data versus Cur concentration was in the range of 0.5–35 μM (y = 0.0162 + 0.0221x, R2 = 0.9927). The LOD was calculated as 76 nM (see Fig. 5
                        ).
